data.description: Welcome to 51 Forest Lane, this bright and sunny 3 bedroom townhouse with a full basement! Freshly painted, new carpets installed throughout, new microwave and vanity in the upstairs bathroom. First level: livingroom, 1/2 bath, eat in kitchen & sliders to yard space. Second level: 3 bedrooms with plenty of closets and one full bath. Basement level: laundry, 3/4 bathroom, closet space, and nice size area for playroom or movie nights! Low HOA fee that includes, pool, tennis, snow removal and outside maintenance. Designated parking spot a few steps from your front door. Conveniently located close to Hylan blvd which provides local and express buses. Make your appointment today, don't miss your chance to own a 3 bedroom home in this gorgeous community!
